com.emc.vipr.model.sys.logging

Class LogMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.emc.vipr.model.sys.logging.LogMessage

  • public class LogMessage
extends java.lang.Object
    Class to encapsulate the data for a log message. Implements the Comparable interface for the purpose of sorting log messages by the log message timestamp.
